company_name: HOHENLOHE'SCHE OBSTVERWERTUNG CARL SCHLIESSMANN NACHF. GMBH & CO. KG
information: The company HOHENLOHE'SCHE OBSTVERWERTUNG CARL SCHLIESSMANN NACHF. GMBH & CO. KG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1911, which operates in the Juices, fruit and vegetable industry. It is based in Schwäbisch Hall, Germany.
